<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#TSJN-01-08-0163-fn-0001-ptr" id="TSJN-01-08-0163-fn-0001">1</a><p>The date, of course, is that of TJs summary; Herries proposal was dated 12 Apr. 1785.</p></div>
